This opcode node type (see the [`znode_op`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/znode_op) type) is used for complex variables in PHP code. For example, the variable `$obj->a` is considered to be a complex variable, however the variable `$a` is not (it is instead an [`IS_CV`](https://phpinternals.net/docs/is_cv) type).

